Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of fuzzy covering rough set model as a mathematical tool for artificial intelligence, which falls under the scope of cs.AI. The paper also proposes new types of approximation operators, which can be applied in machine learning and data mining, making cs.LG and cs.DM likely sub-categories as well. The study of relationships among different types of approximation operators also suggests the paper may be relevant to cs.SI (social and information networks) and cs.IT (information theory).
